This device would seem to be used with '''Frontier Communications'''' VDSL2 service.
"Actiontec" and "06981A" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :An '''Actiontec''' MAC/model label is affixed to the bottom of the board. The MAC begins with 00:18:01. The FW version is noted as 36.128L.00.
The power supply is noted as an '''Actiontec''' STD-12018U1 in the FCC test report. :This is a 12V 1.8A adapter.
